data.description: This attractive two-story has the perfect location for commuting north, south, east or west via I-35 or Highway 2 in southern Iowa.  The structure has a two-year old roof, full basement and newer storage shed to organize garden and lawn tools and lawnmower.  The lottage is almost one acre with room to the west to build your dream garage or sell to a future homebuilder.  It's a great location and a very nice home to consider if you are looking in southern Iowa!!
